overview: The doctor will see you again now – but, as in Part 1, don’t expect any of these horny medics to be satisfied with anything other than a thorough and very intimate examination! Indeed, there’s nothing glib or half-hearted for the patients here; as STAXUS favourites, Nick Vargas, Tom Nutt and Milan Sharp continue to show fresh-faces such as Alex Couzens and Jacob Waterhouse that a top-class medical check-up involves more than a simple “Cough & Drop”. More like open wide, fuck raw and hard, and dump copious amounts of pent-up twink-juice!
title: Raw Medics 2
